    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Happy new year 2011 from Handlino!</p>



<p>It has been a great year of 2010 for Handlino, but that does not stop us

from pushing ourself forward. We have been recently working on a

Ruby desktop application and it is ready just on time.</p>



<p>Yes, our first desktop product is proudly out: <a href="http://compass.handlino.com/">Compass.app</a>.</p>



<p>Compass.app is a quick tool for designers to write <a href="http://compass-style.org/">Compass</a>

stylesheets (an enhanced CSS) easily without resorting to its

command line interface. It&#8217;s cross-platform and runs on Mac,

Windows, and even Linux.</p>



<p>Rapid prototyping is much easier with Compass and Compass.app then use

plain-old CSS. We highly encourge you to familiarize with Compass

because it actually makes fast prototyping fun, and productive.</p>



<p>Please visit Compass.app website at

<a href="http://compass.handlino.com/">compass.handlion.com</a> to take a

look, and be sure to get it with our special new year offer of

only $7 dollars price.</p>
